                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>24<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi>. Augt.</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>Pha.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Rev. Dr. Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I received the proof<lb/> last <add>שבת</add> &amp; returned it on\n                    <date>Sunday</date>.<lb/> I trust it reached you in time.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><sic>Inclosed</sic> the second part<lb/> of the paper on “Jewish\n                doctrine.”<lb/> It grows under my hand, &amp; to<lb/> me appears very interesting.\n                If<lb/> therefore you are not tired of<lb/> it, I will carry it over.\n                <add>?</add><lb/> papers more—if not I will<lb/> squeeze it into one—Please<lb/> let\n                me know which you prefer<lb/> &amp; oblige me with a proof.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I see, you advertise a Bible<lb/> in 18 mo for $2.50—with 20\n                    <add>?</add> to<lb/> those who sell—now I don't sell</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33j39m68/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
