                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>but give away, free gratis<lb/> for nothing—Assuming you<lb/> will allow me the hopes\n                that<lb/> this is an English Bible—please<lb/> send me a copy at your<lb/> earliest\n                convenience</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Rev Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Very Respy</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M J Raphall</persName>\n            </p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_17_23.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 17 No. 23 pages 134 through 135. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
